channel.title: How Many People Could I Hold?
channel.description: How many people could I hold with 500 kbps upload speed and 7000 kbps download speed according to speedtest.net. I got dual 1.8 GHZ processor and 2 GB RAM. I also have Windows Vista Home premium, thanks. Name how many people I COULD hold with ME ALSO on it without me or anyone else lagging, also name with what source. Thanks!
